titles.title: A concurrent resolution correcting the enrollment of H.J.Res.602.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Called up by House Under Suspension of Rules.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 9/22/1988--Introduced. Makes corrections in the enrollment of H.J. Res. 602 (in support of the restoration of a free and independent Cambodia) as it relates to the withdrawal of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam's armed forces from Cambodia and the halt of military equipment to the Khmer Rouge.
